The paper discusses a state-of-the-art text mining method for software engineering research, which suggests relevant papers for researchers to read. This falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of an active learner, which is a machine learning technique, indicating a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper is specifically focused on literature reviews in software engineering (cs.SE).
